Food is above standard with some equal to hotel quality. Thoughtful menu, service is good but may feel a bit stretched during busy hours.

result.adr_address: 2 Kornhill Rd, Quarry Bay, Hong Kong
result.formatted_address: 2 Kornhill Rd, Quarry Bay, Hong Kong
result.name: Aeon

reviews.text:
Best place to buy everything in Hong Kong, especially if you are new here. Food, groceries, furniture, clothing, appliances, liquor and there's an interesting food court. 
You can also apply for a normal VISA credit card.
Very good Japanese department store with a supermarket on the ground floor. Many items are imported from Japan, with reasonable price.

The purchasing experience is worse than Amazon. Salespersons there are mostly redundant as most of them just chitchat with each other and don't really answer your questions or anything. Only person you can ask are the two staff at the cashier. Depending on the kinds of item you are finding, it might worth you a try visiting there but otherwise don't waste your time shopping there.

The overall sales assistants and cashier staff are polite and patient . Nice shopping environment and plenty of goods choices. Curtasy and patience are valuable yet rare in hong kong market. These staff deserve credits.
It is a spacious shopping area in HK.  Pay visit during weekdays is fine.  Avoid to shop there in weekend ( too crowded ).

result.adr_address: 香港鰂魚涌康山道2號
result.name: Aeon Style

reviews.text: 當你行入Aeon Shop 超市，貨品種類及價格與其他超市相比，係好抵超值! 最受歡迎的日常生活用品，例如清潔雙手及厠所板；殺菌用嘅Aeon出品wet tissues, 之前賣到斷市呀，$19.9 150張包裝，搵過其他超市係無得fight👍🥇 另外有滴露金裝浴露優惠裝，真係平到我地係客都難以相信，又係其他超市都難以找到嘅日常必需貨品!👍👍👍真是買平貨嘅購物天堂!🎉🎉🎉

Best place to buy everything in Hong Kong, especially if you are new here. Food, groceries, furniture, clothing, appliances, liquor and there's an interesting food court. 
You can also apply for a normal VISA credit card.
貨物款多，在特定日子有95折。
今日減價，但出奇少人，遊行映响？
Aeon 店每逢星期三是“新鮮日”、有許多特價貨品、主要是超市食品、麵包、日用品等；很受歡迎、人流極多、常有收穫、收錢處排長龍、如有時間、值得到訪、逛逛也不錯！

result.adr_address: 香港康山康山道2號
result.name: Quattro's Kitchen

reviews.text: 👍好食物，👍好招待!
今晚食嗰個 扒餐,伴碟嘅菜裏面有塊綠色嘅布，好似不織布定係洗碗布， 超恐怖。 同佢啲侍應講，講完只係聽到一句對唔住，就攞走咗成碟嘢。到最後尾一啲表示都冇，照樣收銭(包括冇賠償冇扣錢) 當冇事發生咁。好差。 我唔係嗰啲問佢攞著數嘅人， 所以就算數，照畀錢。食物質素都可以，但係好多員工都係part time，所以好多嘢都唔熟，常出錯。但收得咁嘅價錢就應該唔止咁
服務員態度非常好，食物質素高。
點咗 雞扒午餐 跟 蕃茄湯及飲品，中等價錢食物質數一般。
食物同菜單圖片上差好遠。同食毛毛意大利，可能好過佢。
